Actually, one more thing: `sodium_utils` is not a great name. Move the definition of `crypto_mem*` into the separate file, so you get something like:
```c
void crypto_memzero(void *data, size_t length)
{
#ifndef VANILLA_NACL
    sodium_memzero(data, length);
#else
    // body of current sodium_memzero here
#endif
}
```
and the same for `crypto_memcmp`.
